</p><p class="- topic/p ">The level-sensor in the printhead suddenly measures an empty printhead while not jetting or receiving pressure-pulses. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">This error happens when ink is leaking out of the printhead. In most cases this related to a pressure failure inside the printhead due to a blocked air-tube. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Often this error is proceeded by MRE250001. 
